Three million views in six minutes.

47:21.541 --> 47:23.083
- That's gotta be a record, right?
- Mm.

47:23.750 --> 47:25.291
Good work, man!

47:25.291 --> 47:28.125
- Hey, kiss my ass, Pewdiepie.

