48:41.666 --> 48:43.416
Ernest Scheller isn't dead.

48:44.416 --> 48:46.166
That guy used to live
in your house though.

48:46.166 --> 48:48.541
I cross-referenced, like,
a bunch of records to make sure.

48:48.541 --> 48:50.333
- So, who's our Ernest?
- Mmm.

48:51.208 --> 48:53.416
But I bet my left nut
that guy knows who he is.

48:53.416 --> 48:56.458
- You bet your what?
- That Ernest lives somewhere in Oklahoma.

48:56.458 --> 48:58.291
I'm still trying to find out where.

48:58.291 --> 49:01.750
But he used to own this dive bar
that's still around.

49:02.791 --> 49:04.416
Oh shit! That's like a mile from us.

49:04.416 --> 49:06.708
Yeah, I know. What if we took him there?

49:06.708 --> 49:07.666
Who?

49:08.791 --> 49:10.250
- Our Ernest?
- Yeah.

49:10.250 --> 49:11.708
Maybe they knew each other.

49:11.708 --> 49:14.041
Maybe it was like a hangout,
and there's a trigger there.

49:14.041 --> 49:16.083
Joy, he can't leave the house.

49:16.708 --> 49:18.666
He... He's stuck there.

49:19.625 --> 49:20.458
Are you sure?

49:24.291 --> 49:28.416
- Ernest! I love you, Ernest!

49:34.833 --> 49:37.666
Nonexclusive?
Are you kidding me, man?

49:37.666 --> 49:40.458
Look, I'm already runnin' original content
through my channel

49:40.458 --> 49:43.541
and making three times what you offered,
so think about what you just said.

49:43.541 --> 49:46.500
Think of a number and call me back,
all right? Bye.

49:48.458 --> 49:49.958
Frank, can you get the door, please?

49:49.958 --> 49:52.791
No, look, I'm serious.
Like, an Ernest cartoon would be amazing.

49:52.791 --> 49:54.750
But I want it to be
something like Adult Swim.

49:54.750 --> 49:57.666
Have you ever seen a naked ghost?
I haven't. What would that look like?

49:58.583 --> 50:01.791
- Frank, are you gonna get the door?
- What parts would a naked ghost have?

50:04.791 --> 50:06.166
Okay, I'm coming!

50:10.375 --> 50:12.791
- Sorry. We're not talking to the press.

50:16.625 --> 50:18.875
Just a few minutes of your time,
if I may, please?

50:20.208 --> 50:22.958
And Joy was doing all this research.

50:22.958 --> 50:26.375
Found out that the guy who lived here
used to own a bar not too far from here.

50:26.375 --> 50:29.125
So we figured,
if we could get you to the bar,

50:29.125 --> 50:30.625
maybe you'd remember something.

50:30.625 --> 50:32.291
Oh!

50:32.291 --> 50:33.541
Joy.

50:34.125 --> 50:35.125
Come on.

50:36.625 --> 50:38.125
You're right. Sorry.

50:39.708 --> 50:41.833
Okay, so we figured
that if we could get...

50:44.333 --> 50:46.416
It's so cold!

50:47.833 --> 50:49.208
Oh my God, I'm sorry. It's...

50:49.208 --> 50:50.833
I love this. I'm-- I'm a fan.

50:50.833 --> 50:52.708
I just-- I know I'm being annoying.

50:52.708 --> 50:55.375
Just, this is a thing
that's actually happening, and...

50:56.916 --> 50:59.041
Sorry.

51:00.083 --> 51:00.916
Anyway.

51:02.291 --> 51:03.500
We need to get you outside.

51:04.916 --> 51:06.875
Are you sure you can't leave?

51:13.500 --> 51:14.416
Have you tried?

51:16.416 --> 51:17.625
I mean, really tried.

51:20.666 --> 51:21.500
Okay.

51:23.666 --> 51:24.708
Listen, Ernest.

51:26.291 --> 51:27.166
I get it.

51:27.833 --> 51:30.958
You've been here a long time,

51:30.958 --> 51:33.916
and the world is such a scary place.

51:35.416 --> 51:38.666
Believe me, sometimes it terrifies me too,

51:39.958 --> 51:42.125
but there aren't any answers
left in this house.

51:42.833 --> 51:45.208
If we're gonna find out who you are...

51:47.083 --> 51:48.333
what happened to you...

51:50.708 --> 51:51.916
it's out there.

51:54.250 --> 51:58.333
I am so sorry to come over here uninvited.

51:58.333 --> 52:01.958
- I would've called, you know, but--
- Sorry. What's the point of this visit?

52:03.916 --> 52:07.500
Back in the late '90s,
I was recruited by the CIA

52:07.500 --> 52:11.750
to spearhead a program called Wizard Clip.

52:12.875 --> 52:13.791
Wizard Clip?

52:14.875 --> 52:18.708
Is that like, y'all just get high
and watch Harry Potter movies and...

52:18.708 --> 52:19.625
Babe.

52:19.625 --> 52:21.541
Wizard Clip was a textbook spook op,

52:21.541 --> 52:24.375
hidden from most echelons
of the government.

52:24.375 --> 52:26.833
Our field was paranormal psychology,

52:26.833 --> 52:31.291
but our orders were
to find and apprehend a ghost.

52:35.541 --> 52:37.666
There's nothing to be afraid of.
I promise.

52:38.208 --> 52:39.125
Okay?

52:57.875 --> 53:00.375
Hey. Hey, hey, hey. Hey.

53:00.375 --> 53:02.291
Listen to me. Listen.

53:04.333 --> 53:06.291
You're not alone anymore, Ernest.

53:07.875 --> 53:10.125
I'm right here with you
every step of the way.

53:12.166 --> 53:13.250
You got this.

54:04.916 --> 54:06.875
Soon as word got out that

54:06.875 --> 54:12.125
millions of taxpayers' dollars
were being spent on woo-woo science,

54:12.625 --> 54:14.750
we were abruptly shut down,

54:14.750 --> 54:18.583
and the agency
threw me under the proverbial bus.

54:20.208 --> 54:21.666
A sacrificial lamb.

54:22.291 --> 54:23.541
It was soul-crushing.

54:27.458 --> 54:29.708
But then along came Ernest.

54:29.708 --> 54:34.041
Okay. Thank you so much for coming over,
but as you can see, we are busy.

54:35.041 --> 54:36.041
I'd like to see him.

54:36.041 --> 54:37.458
That's not gonna happen.

54:38.208 --> 54:41.625
I don't think you understand
the gravity of your situation.

54:41.625 --> 54:44.000
These entities, they are dangerous.

54:44.000 --> 54:45.458
I'd like you to leave, please.

54:45.458 --> 54:48.916
They may present kindly,
but they are never who they say they are.

54:48.916 --> 54:51.750
- I'm not gonna ask you--
- Your son Kevin.

54:51.750 --> 54:54.416
He's close to it.
I've seen it in the videos. He's at risk!

54:54.416 --> 54:56.041
All right! That's enough! Now, get out!

54:56.041 --> 54:59.458
This is a matter of national security.
I have a right to be here.

54:59.458 --> 55:01.208
Then come back with a warrant.

55:01.208 --> 55:04.875
But until that time,
get the hell out of my house.

55:11.041 --> 55:11.958
I'll be back.

55:12.833 --> 55:13.666
That's a promise.

55:28.666 --> 55:29.541
It's him!

55:29.541 --> 55:30.708
Shit!

55:30.708 --> 55:32.958
Oh my God! It's him! It's Ernest!

55:32.958 --> 55:34.541
- It's him!

55:47.333 --> 55:48.666
Ernest! Ernest!

56:20.375 --> 56:21.666
Shit!

56:26.083 --> 56:26.916
Dick move!

56:26.916 --> 56:27.833
Come on.

56:28.625 --> 56:29.500
In there!

