57:25.291 --> 57:27.166
What?
Why didn't he do that sooner?

57:27.166 --> 57:29.000
I don't know. Come on. We gotta go.

57:29.916 --> 57:31.083
This is bullshit.

57:31.083 --> 57:33.791
Well... [moans] ...I hate to remind you

57:33.791 --> 57:36.000
about a little thing
called the Fourth Amendment.

57:36.000 --> 57:37.625
They're harboring a terrorist.

57:37.625 --> 57:41.875
I'm not sure a ghost
would legally qualify as a terrorist.

57:44.625 --> 57:46.208
They'll make a mistake.

57:48.125 --> 57:50.333
Careless people always do.

57:53.500 --> 57:55.041
And when that happens...

57:57.625 --> 57:58.791
we'll be ready.

58:11.291 --> 58:13.416
Chuck E. Cheese
is down the street, kiddos.

58:13.958 --> 58:16.666
Do you know this guy?
He used to work here back in the day.

58:16.666 --> 58:18.833
This place has had over a dozen owners.

58:19.500 --> 58:21.125
Can't we just look around for a minute?

58:21.125 --> 58:24.541
Sweetie, I could lose my liquor license.
You gotta go.

58:26.500 --> 58:28.458
Come on. This is stupid. Let's just go.

58:32.208 --> 58:34.208
Hey, wait.

58:35.666 --> 58:37.166
Let me see that picture again.

58:45.000 --> 58:45.833
There.

58:52.041 --> 58:52.875
Oh my God.

58:57.041 --> 58:59.333
See? There is a connection.

58:59.333 --> 59:00.250
I knew it.

59:01.125 --> 59:03.166
Hold on. You're that kid, aren't you?

59:03.166 --> 59:05.666
Uh, I'm sorry. I don't...
I don't know what you're talking about.

59:05.666 --> 59:08.041
With the ghost in your house.
It is you! Holy shit!

59:08.041 --> 59:10.333
Okay, thank you for your time.
We have to go.

59:12.250 --> 59:13.375
You're a genius.

59:13.958 --> 59:16.458
This Scheller guy
has to know who Ernest really is.

59:16.458 --> 59:18.625
And to think that you doubted me.

59:18.625 --> 59:19.833
I never doubted you.

59:20.333 --> 59:22.458
- Now we just have to find where he is.
-  Mom!

59:22.458 --> 59:24.083
There's a ghost over there!

59:24.625 --> 59:26.125
That's nice, sweetie.

59:28.541 --> 59:29.375
Ernest.

59:31.041 --> 59:32.500
Ernest, what's wrong?

59:35.625 --> 59:36.583
Ernest.

59:42.416 --> 59:44.000
-  Ernest!

59:48.625 --> 59:49.541
Ernest!

59:59.666 --> 1:00:01.375
Hi, Daddy.

1:00:05.125 --> 1:00:06.208
Junebug.

1:00:14.791 --> 1:00:16.083
Shit.

1:00:16.083 --> 1:00:17.875
Mom!

1:00:20.041 --> 1:00:22.291
Ernest, come on! We gotta go!

1:00:22.833 --> 1:00:23.708
Ernest!

1:00:25.791 --> 1:00:26.916
Ernest!

1:00:28.458 --> 1:00:29.541
<i>Ernest!</i>

1:00:34.541 --> 1:00:36.291
<i>Ernest, come on! We gotta go!</i>

