I think a warrant just fell
right into our lap.

1:00:44.791 --> 1:00:46.541
"Ernest The Not-So-Friendly Ghost."

1:00:46.541 --> 1:00:48.958
"Paranormal Whacktivity."

1:00:48.958 --> 1:00:50.416
They think he's a monster now.

1:00:50.416 --> 1:00:53.833
He saw something out there.
Like he was remembering something.

1:00:53.833 --> 1:00:56.500
Well, it looks like
he's trying to kidnap Shirley Temple!

1:00:56.500 --> 1:00:58.416
And why didn't you tell me
he could go outside?

1:00:58.416 --> 1:01:00.000
That should've been my exclusive.

1:01:00.000 --> 1:01:01.500
You're not listening to me.

1:01:01.500 --> 1:01:02.666
He said a name,

1:01:02.666 --> 1:01:05.333
it was, uh, June something.

1:01:05.333 --> 1:01:07.541
- So what?
- So maybe that's why he's stuck here.

1:01:08.541 --> 1:01:10.791
Something happened to him. Something bad.

1:01:10.791 --> 1:01:15.083
Maybe if we help him remember more,
he can, uh, cross over.

1:01:15.083 --> 1:01:16.500
Cross over?

1:01:16.500 --> 1:01:20.833
We don't want him to cross over, Kevin.
We need him here with us.

1:01:22.041 --> 1:01:23.875
You really
don't give a shit about him, do you?

1:01:23.875 --> 1:01:26.916
I give a shit about us!
This is about our future.

1:01:26.916 --> 1:01:30.041
This is about Fulton's college tuition.
It's about yours.

1:01:30.041 --> 1:01:31.375
Don't make this about us.

1:01:32.625 --> 1:01:33.708
It's about you.

1:01:34.541 --> 1:01:35.750
Always is.

1:01:36.375 --> 1:01:38.333
Hey, I'm not finished talking to you, man.

1:01:45.250 --> 1:01:46.833
You didn't hear a word he said.

