400 miles from here, give or take.

1:04:23.166 --> 1:04:24.500
Shit. That's far.

1:04:25.083 --> 1:04:27.583
We'll take driving shifts.
We'll make it.

1:04:29.000 --> 1:04:31.041
Okay.
I appreciate the optimism.

1:04:35.916 --> 1:04:38.541
You look... different.

1:04:39.166 --> 1:04:40.750
- I do?
- Yeah.

1:04:41.833 --> 1:04:43.208
Being an outlaw suits you.

1:04:44.625 --> 1:04:45.625
Thanks.

1:04:52.250 --> 1:04:55.125
Um, we should...
we should probably get going.

1:04:55.125 --> 1:04:56.208
Mmm.

